    <item>
      <title>AUCTF 2020 Writeup - House of Madness</title>
      <link>https://www.raffaeleflorio.com/post/house-of-madness-auctf2020/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.raffaeleflorio.com/post/house-of-madness-auctf2020/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;intro&#34;&gt;Intro&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This is the third pwn challenge. It was solved 100 times and it was worth 897 points.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Description:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the House of Madness. Can you pwn your way to the keys to get the relic?&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;nc challenges.auctf.com 30012&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Note: ASLR is disabled for this challenge&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You could download the binary &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.raffaeleflorio.com/ctf/auctf2020/binary/house_of_madness&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$ sha256sum ./house_of_madness&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;15b1a68ae0e1d4eee4f917cc92412d90fd3a4adbb5a55a83b115e0f438baaf93  house_of_madness&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id=&#34;exploitation&#34;&gt;Exploitation&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;When we launch the program shows a banner and it asks us to make a choice. I tried at this point, without success, a classic buffer overflow.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AUCTF 2020 Writeup - Thanksgiving Dinner</title>
      <link>https://www.raffaeleflorio.com/post/thanksgiving-dinner-auctf2020/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
